Running the command

#> python3 testsuite.py

under the directory tests/ invokes swi3s_visualizer.py for all the configuration files
in tests/test_cfgs in batch mode.
Output JSONs are put under tests/test_outs/, that must not exist, so the advice is to run
the regression this way:

#> rmdir test_outs/ && python3 testsuite.py

